		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hello, I can recomend the other video where Warren is talking about bass recording. It&#8217;s here on the courses section. the thing he is doing there ist just putting little compression and EQ during recording so the print is already compressed when recorded. I think it&#8217;s better then doing compression after because you can hear the exact sound while recording so you can adjust your playing to that exact sound you are getting. </p>
